column2: Creemers Stefan, 2021, The resource-constrained project scheduling problem: New benchmark results, 17th International Workshop on Project Management and Scheduling (PMS 2021), Toulouse (France), April 21-23, 2021.
Coded in C++, compiled in Visual Studio 2019 (64 bit), and run on a single thread of an Intel I9-9900K CPU running at 3.6GHz with 128GB of RAM.
